      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested, all from the same production lot. Dimensional inspection of all specimens confirmed conformance to drawing tolerances. Sample size sufficient to characterize inter-specimen variability for uncertainty quantification."
